cast.overview: A controlling father’s attempts to ensure that his two children succeed in high school backfire after his son experiences a career-ending sports injury. Their familial bonds are eventually placed under severe strain by an unexpected tragedy.
cast.title: Waves

details.biography: Carter Owen Harcek is an American actor. Born in Midland, Michigan, USA in 2009. He started his career at 9 years old with his first feature film. He developed a passion for acting and modeling during that filming. Carter lives in Midland with his mom, dad and brother. His passion is acting, but he also loves playing baseball and basketball. Carter strives to develop his acting and modeling career throughout the years.
details.name: Carter Harcek
